column2: "You seem to sure have come a long way to get here."
"Part of the reason we were able to investigate this far in is because of your efforts."
"It's because you were able to pass the request presented by the Dragonkin."
"I did my part, but it's not enough to be praised for or stand out."
"I wonder if it would be possible for me to do what you did..."
"Anyways, since we've managed to get here, it seems like a good idea to investigate as much as possible."
"Hm? Light? He seems to be busy lately, I haven't seen him in a while."
"Either that or, there's no more need for him to monitor me anymore."
"Maybe that was saying to much. I'm going to get back to investigating."
